{"tid":1075094,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國海軍陸戰隊在沖繩演練二戰奪島戰術   針對台灣海峽","createTime":"2019-03-24T00:30:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-27T06:27:44.000Z","uid":35790,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"ba63551a397ec6c2666d2fe7b5c9789948d018c4","tid":1075094,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T00:30:30.000Z","msg":"美軍演練二戰奪島戰術 針對台海<br />\n<a href=\"https://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/china_world/20190324/mobile/odn-20190324-0324_00178_003.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fchina_world%2F20190324%2Fmobile%2Fodn-20190324-0324_00178_003.html&d=6SPFYKHnGSG2Q49qavPU8l3VpWtqcNNCzs9YdIyDBYU%3D&h=3a5aa9c1\" target=\"_blank\">https://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/china_world/20190324/mobile/odn-20190324-0324_00178_003.html</a>"},{"pid":"c71cd4dc96f6809396ec385e93b442c9983995da","tid":1075094,"uid":35790,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T00:32:01.000Z","msg":"因應與中國爆發衝突 美軍在太平洋演練奪島<br />\n<br />\n2019-03-23<br />\n<br />\n〔編譯成良／綜合報導〕美軍二戰期間在太平洋運用跳島戰術（island hopping）對抗日軍攻擊，70幾年後的今天，美軍在太平洋演練奪島並重溫這項戰術，以因應與中國可能發生的衝突。<br />\n<br />\n據「商業內幕」（Business Insider）網站報導，美軍陸戰隊21日宣布，美軍第31陸戰隊遠征分隊（31st Marine Expeditionary Unit）上週協同空軍和陸軍的作戰和後勤單位，在日本沖繩縣西部外海的伊江島，聯合演練一系列模擬奪島行動。<br />\n<br />\n這項演習是美軍陸戰隊為完善「遠征前進作戰基地」（expeditionary advanced base operation）概念所做的努力之一，而這個概念就是二戰時期跳島戰術的現代版。<br />\n<br />\n演習中，陸戰隊奪取伊江島機場後，美軍迅速建立前方武裝和加油據點，供陸戰隊的F-35B戰機等其它軍力資產使用，而C-130J運輸機也運來火砲等武器。隨後，美軍用這些火砲執行長距離精準射擊，而F-35B戰機則以「制導炸彈」執行遠程攻擊行動。制導炸彈是指發射後能控制彈道並導向目標的航空炸彈。<br />\n<br />\n陸戰隊在聲明中說：「這整個任務模擬取得前方據點的過程，以便供後方部隊經由快速重新部署，執行進一步軍事行動。」<br />\n<br />\n北京在南海地區的領土主張愈發強硬，造島及島嶼軍事化行動，升高了美國的警惕。美國國防部在去年的《國防戰略報告》指出，中國正在南海島嶼上建立軍事設施，並試圖將其勢力延伸到第一島鏈之外。<br />\n<br />\n美國參謀長聯席會議主席鄧福德（Joseph Dunford）上將上週告訴參議院軍事委員會，對美國而言，能投射力量以因應中國，至為重要，而陸戰隊的傳統任務之一就是奪取前方基地。<br />\n<br />\n鄧福德說：「如果你把太平洋的島鏈看成我們可以投射力量的平台，那就是陸戰隊的歷史任務，這個任務在（應對）中國的局面中是非常相關的。」<br />\n&lt;自由時報&gt;"},{"pid":"2b170ca2f694aafbd84be166fb8b61f64111aa8d","tid":1075094,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T00:43:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7771db0d76dc240762274f327463d9ca8c6e5a7a","tid":1075094,"uid":179467,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T00:48:23.000Z","msg":"Island hopping死咗咁多人仲用 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n俾我係侵侵就炸鳩咗三峽大壩或核平上海 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1ca279e10d2c4bb01d85322d76070430b577bee","tid":1075094,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T03:39:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca8db462618294213a53a2d96dcdcf8e6adfd095","tid":1075094,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T10:54:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57638f29b4a91cdad08ef2500df0ea8898c6ad00","tid":1075094,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T14:37:34.000Z","msg":"如果kmt執政<br />\n接受和平統一<br />\n一國兩制<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c3b6091b2588b8723e7ed0943fa2a16f47dc0a4","tid":1075094,"uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T14:42:50.000Z","msg":"打未呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56335105becd50f8bc3dd7ed4e35dea2fa7ccf48","tid":1075094,"uid":235174,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T16:52:43.000Z","msg":"共軍作出反擊<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/fj4dVFa.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Ffj4dVFa.gif&h=4187d241&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3a6fcdd06f241a43974f9f1cd